<section class="wizard__section wizard__section--faq">
<h1 class="wizard__title">Choose your high-speed wireless Internet</h1>
<div class="faq__description">
<div class="row v-gutters" style="--gutter-y: 50px; --gutter-x: 20px">
<div class="col-sm-4 col-12">
<div class="wizard-plan wizard__item wizard__item--noprice">
<img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0103/2847/3658/t/130/assets/faq-01.jpg?v=140601820471777833041679746530" alt="Nomad Internet" width="562" height="362" loading="lazy" class="item__image">
<div class="item__content">
<h3 class="item__title">Which Plan Is Right for Me?</h3>

<div class="item__description" data-collapse="... View more" data-collapse-height="70" style="overflow: hidden; height: 70px; transition: all 0.6s ease 0s;">
<p>
Each plan is designed to fit a different primary use. While all plans have unlimited 4G and 5G data,
it is best to pick a plan based on what your needs! The primary difference between each plan is
outlined below:
</p>

<ul>
<li>
Residential Plan: Designed for home use, includes unlimited data, and download speeds of up to
100Mbps.
</li>
<li>
Travel Plan: Designed for use in the home and on the go, includes unlimited data and download
speeds of up to 100Mbps, AND you can pause and unpause your monthly billing!
</li>
<li>
Business Plan: Designed for high demand uses such as business and gaming. Includes unlimited data
and download speeds of up to 200Mbps!
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="col-sm-4 col-12">
<div class="wizard-plan wizard__item wizard__item--noprice">
<img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0103/2847/3658/t/130/assets/faq-02.jpg?v=116919464870281962681679746531" alt="Nomad Internet" width="562" height="362" loading="lazy" class="item__image">

<div class="item__content">
<h3 class="item__title">Which Device Is Right for Me?</h3>

<div class="item__description" data-collapse="... View more" data-collapse-height="70" style="overflow: hidden; height: 70px; transition: all 0.6s ease 0s;">
<p>
The three main Nomad Modems we offer can be used at the same places but have significant
differences.
</p>

<ul>
<li>The Nomad Air is small, light, and can be used anywhere you are.</li>
<li>
The Nomad Raptor is larger than the Air, but still portable, and is built with the strongest
indoor antennas to achieve faster speeds.
</li>
<li>
The Nomad Ark is an “Outdoor Modem” with the furthest range a wireless modem can possibly
provide. Using Nomad Ark is more powerful than a cell booster. Simply put, if it is “possible”
to get the internet in a remote location, it will happen with a Nomad Ark.
</li>
</ul>

<p>All our devices ship pre-configured ready to plug in.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="col-sm-4 col-12">
<div class="wizard-plan wizard__item wizard__item--noprice">
<img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0103/2847/3658/t/130/assets/faq-03.jpg?v=142142617986317178731679746531" alt="Nomad Internet" width="562" height="362" loading="lazy" class="item__image">

<div class="item__content">
<h3 class="item__title">What if it Doesn’t Work for Me?</h3>

<div class="item__description" data-collapse="... View more" data-collapse-height="70" style="overflow: hidden; height: 70px; transition: all 0.6s ease 0s;">
<p>
If the plan you initially choose does not connect or is slower than expected, we have you covered!
You can change plans until you get the speeds you need, and we will ship you a new Nomad Modem until
allows you to return your device for a full refund.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="wizard__section-footer">
<a id="btn-1" class="btn outline" href="#wizard-plans">Continue to plan selection →</a>
</div>
</section>

